//! Fail-closed FLUX txt2img admission driver.
//!
//! `flux-probe` proves KNOT plumbing with a deterministic smoke renderer. This
//! module is the stricter FLUX runtime surface: it validates the full KNOT,
//! parses Unsound scheduling options, admits native carrier-bridge evidence
//! separately, and refuses prompt-faithful visible-image admission until exact
//! T5/DiT/VAE stages are wired.

